Articles.Content: I've been playing Kerbal Space Program for a few years now, give or take. I've been too busy having fun to count. And I recently did something I've wanted to do for a long time. With my first science mode landing on Eeloo I have finally landed on every body in the Kerbolar System and finished the game. I just wanted to take time to thank everyone who worked on this wonderful game and maintaining it for so long. here's to another 10 years of KSP!
Good on ya! That ship looks snazzy
